data.description: Move-In Ready!  This Beautiful Home has Tile throughout the 1st floor and Brand New LVP Flooring in the 2nd Floor Bedrooms, hallway and loft!  Located conveniently close to Beaches, Bases, Schools and Shopping - Just 3 miles West Of Hurlburt field in Mary Esther where property taxes are LOW!  This Mediterranean style, 2 story home is part of a well maintained, quiet neighborhood. The HVAC was new in 2023, saving $$$ on Utility Bills!  There are Two Living Areas: One at the entry with Soaring 24ft ceilings and lots of natural light & another Living Area that opens to the Elegant Kitchen and has a Cozy Fireplace!  The Kitchen has abundant Wood Cabinets, a Breakfast Bar with storage, Granite Counter Tops, Large Pantry & updated Stainless Appliances - including a Double Oven!  Lovely plantation shutters compliment the interior crown molding.  The First floor also has a half bath, 4 more storage areas, Laundry area, Utility sink + full cabinet suite in garage. Upstairs, there is a bonus room/loft, a Spacious Master Suite including Sitting/Nursery area and a large Master Bath with Granite, Double Vanities, Garden Tub and Separate Shower.  The Additional Guest Bedrooms are nicely sized and the Guest Bath has Granite, Double Vanities and Tile. There is a Large 2-Car Garage, Lawn Pump and Sprinkler System. The Back Yard is Privacy Fenced with an Oversized Paver Patio with plenty of room to entertain!
